    <item>
      <title>莫斯科维奇称法国需要稳定，而不是新总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/france-needs-stability-not-new-president-moscovici-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国国家审计长皮埃尔·莫斯科维奇表示，法国需要政治稳定来解决高额预算赤字问题，并警告不要在 2027 年埃马纽埃尔·马克龙任期结束前提前举行总统大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/france-needs-stability-not-new-president-moscovici-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 08:09:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦央行行长将俄罗斯黑客视为银行面临的主要风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/danish-central-banker-sees-russia-hackers-as-key-risk-to-lenders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦央行高级官员表示，针对北欧银行的网络攻击可能是由与俄罗斯有关的黑客实施的，这对该地区的金融稳定构成了最大威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/danish-central-banker-sees-russia-hackers-as-key-risk-to-lenders</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 07:40:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度监管机构正在调查阿达尼是否违反信息披露规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/india-sebi-looking-into-whether-adani-flouted-disclosure-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度资本市场监管机构正在调查阿达尼集团是否违反了强制披露市场动态信息的规定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/india-sebi-looking-into-whether-adani-flouted-disclosure-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 07:32:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三菱日联银行解雇一名员工，因其从客户保险箱中盗窃 1300 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/mufg-fires-worker-for-13-million-theft-from-clients-safe-boxes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三菱日联金融集团表示，已解雇一名员工，该员工涉嫌从大约 60 名客户的保险箱中窃取高达 20 亿日元（1300 万美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/mufg-fires-worker-for-13-million-theft-from-clients-safe-boxes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 07:32:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称 Greatview 董事长正考虑与 Cloudview 进行竞标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/greatview-chairman-said-to-weigh-counterbid-with-cloudview</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，纷美无菌包装股份有限公司董事长正在与中国私募股权公司云景资本洽谈联手收购这家乳制品包装公司，此举可能会引发竞购战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/greatview-chairman-said-to-weigh-counterbid-with-cloudview</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 07:15:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Gensler 退出计划导致美国证券交易委员会瞄准的加密代币数量激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/crypto-tokens-xrp-ada-sol-targeted-by-sec-jump-on-gensler-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国证券交易委员会主席、业界头号反对者加里·根斯勒 (Gary Gensler) 宣布计划辞职后，被美国证券交易委员会标记为未注册证券的数字资产正在上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/crypto-tokens-xrp-ada-sol-targeted-by-sec-jump-on-gensler-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 07:07:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
