      <title>科技股业绩疲软打击市场人气，中国股市暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/chinese-stocks-slump-as-weak-tech-earnings-hit-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五下午，中国股市抛售加剧，令人失望的科技股收益进一步打击了因对唐纳德·特朗普即将回归的担忧而本已疲软的市场人气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/chinese-stocks-slump-as-weak-tech-earnings-hit-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 06:50:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
