      <title>俄乌战争升级，油价有望每周上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于俄罗斯和乌克兰之间的敌对情绪升级，油价创下自十月初以来的最大单周涨幅。]]></description>
